@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Welcome to the Library Management System";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="jumbotron text-center bg-light shadow-sm p-5 rounded">
        <h1 class="display-4 font-weight-bold">Welcome to the Library Management System</h1>
        <p class="lead text-muted mt-3">"Books are a uniquely portable magic." – Stephen King</p>
        <hr class="my-4">
        <p class="text-secondary">
            Explore a vast collection of books that fuel your imagination, expand your knowledge, and enrich your life. Whether you're seeking wisdom, adventure, or relaxation, a book is always a perfect companion. Join us in discovering new worlds, one page at a time.
        </p>
        <a asp-area="" asp-controller="Book" asp-action="Index" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mt-3">Browse Books</a>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Why Should We Read Books?</h2>
            <p>Books offer us knowledge, insight, and a way to escape to different worlds. They inspire, educate, and entertain us. Reading develops our critical thinking skills, enriches our vocabulary, and allows us to experience life through another's perspective. Whether it's fiction or non-fiction, books challenge our minds and help us grow.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h2>Books: Our Best Friends</h2>
            <p>Books are our silent companions. They never judge, but they offer endless wisdom. In every phase of life, whether we're feeling joyful or troubled, we can always turn to books for comfort and guidance. They open doors to new ideas and help us understand ourselves and the world around us better. In a world full of distractions, books remain steadfast, waiting for us to engage with their pages.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
